{"lemma":"صَعِيدٌ","slug":"صَعِيدٌ","root":"ص.ع.د","root_slug":"ص-ع-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ع-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"صَعِيد","root":"صعد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24323"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%AF%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"highland, upland, plateau"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sˤa.ʕiːd/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24323","headword_ar":"صَعِيدٌ","root":"SEd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"High,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated, land"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated, land"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground, above such as is low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depressed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"even land"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground:"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1689},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"even land"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground, without any trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desert such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHoraA='","text_ar":"صَحْرَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surface of the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, Zj, S, A, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether it be dust"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"otherwise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"Zj says, I know not any difference of opinion among the lexicologists on this point: (Msb:) [such is said to be its meaning in the Kur iv. 46 and v. 9; and therefore in performing the act termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~ayam~am","text_ar":"التَّيَمَّم"},{"kind":"text","text":",] a man should strike his hands upon the surface of the earth, and not care whether there be in chat place dust or not: (Zj:) [hence] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAra Siytuka fiY Alqariybi waAlbaEiydi wabalaga munotahaY","text_ar":"طَارَ صِيتُكَ فِى القَرِيبِ وَالبَعِيدِ وَبَلَغَ مُنْتَهَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~aEiydi","text_ar":"الصَّعِيدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thy fame has flown through the near and the distant"},{"kind":"text","text":"regions,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and reached the extremity of the surface of the earth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (A:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaEiydN","text_ar":"صَعِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"itself; (IAar, A, L;) as in the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayoka biAlS~aEiydi","text_ar":"عَلَيْكَ بِالصَّعِيدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sit thou upon the earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good earth"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land, not mixed with sand nor with salt soil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, S, L, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is pure, upon the surface of the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has come forth from within it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus accord. to Az in the Kur iv. 46 and v. 9, in the opinion of most of the learned: (Msb:) or only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth containing dust;"},{"kind":"text","text":"not applied to a coarse, nor to a fine,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baToHaA='","text_ar":"بَطْحَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"; nor to a coarse"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaviyb","text_ar":"كَثِيب"},{"kind":"text","text":"; although it be mixed with dust: (Esh-Sháfi'ee, L:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuEudN","text_ar":"صُعُدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuEudaAtN","text_ar":"صُعُدَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, K,) the latter a pl. pl. (Msb, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an ample, place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A road,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb, K,) whether wide or narrow: (L:) pls. as above (L, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuEodaAnN","text_ar":"صُعْدَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iy~aAkumo waAlquEuwda biAlS~uEudaAti","text_ar":"اـِيَّاكُمْ وَالقُعُودَ بِالصُّعُدَاتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_il~aAmano A^ad~aY Haq~ahaA","text_ar":"اـِلَّامَنْ اَدَّى حَقَّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Beware ye of sitting in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by, the roads, save he who performs the duty relating thereto:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[respecting which duty see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariyqN","text_ar":"طَرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuEudaAt","text_ar":"صُعُدَات"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuEudN","text_ar":"صُعُدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaEiydN","text_ar":"صَعِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, as some say, it is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuEodapN","text_ar":"صُعْدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A court,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an open space, before the door of a house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place through which men pass in front of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A grave."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, Mtr, L, K.)"}],"source_refs":["L","Lth","A","Msb","Zj","Fr","S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}